  ],
  "instructions": [
    "In a large pot, combine the chicken broth, soy sauce, Shaoxing wine, and sliced ginger, and bring to a boil over high heat.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and simmer for 10 minutes.",
    "Add the pork slices to the pot and cook for 2 minutes.",
    "Add the orange segments to the pot and cook for an additional 2 minutes.",
    "Stir in the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Season the hot pot with salt and pepper to taste.",
    "Ladle the hot pot into bowls and garnish with chopped green onions.",
    "Drizzle the sesame oil over the top of each bowl.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy."
  ],
